    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Areas of land or water set apart for the protection of natural landscapes or wildlife, or for the rearing of game or fish; in some preserves, limited hunting is permitted.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
